1. *Uplašio* se da neće biti spreman na ispit. (He was afraid he wouldn't be ready for the exam.)

2. Ona je *uplašena* da će joj se dogoditi nešto loše. (She was scared that something bad would happen to her.)

3. *Uplašili* su se kada su čuli zvuk iz podruma. (They were scared when they heard the sound from the basement.)

4. On je bio *uplašen* da će biti kaznjen. (He was afraid he would be punished.)

5. Oni su *uplašeno* gledali u tamu. (They were looking fearfully into the darkness.)